WEBVTT

00:08.119 --> 00:13.640
<font color="#ffffff">This programme contains some</font>
<font color="#ffffff">scenes of a sexual nature.</font>

00:13.640 --> 00:15.640
<font color="#ffffff">He looks awful.</font>

00:15.640 --> 00:18.800
<font color="#ffff00">Nothing to worry about,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Your Highness. I'm sure of it.</font>

00:18.800 --> 00:21.680
<font color="#ffff00">Your diagnosis? </font><font color="#00ffff">Mild concussion.</font>

00:21.680 --> 00:24.240
<font color="#ffff00">Caused, no doubt, by the fall.</font>

00:25.200 --> 00:27.360
<font color="#00ff00">I didn't fall.</font>

00:27.360 --> 00:29.080
<font color="#00ff00">I was hit.</font>

00:29.080 --> 00:30.560
<font color="#ffffff">Careful!</font>

00:30.560 --> 00:32.280
<font color="#ffff00">Your Highness. </font><font color="#00ff00">Clothes!</font>

00:34.680 --> 00:37.600
<font color="#00ff00">Tell the king I want to see him.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">You're not going anywhere.</font>

00:37.600 --> 00:41.080
<font color="#00ff00">I need to talk to my brother.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">What on earth for?</font>

00:42.920 --> 00:46.280
<font color="#00ff00">The mask. </font><font color="#ffffff">What mask?</font>
<font color="#ffffff">What are you talking about?</font>

00:48.160 --> 00:49.800
<font color="#00ff00">His eyes.</font>

00:50.880 --> 00:54.720
<font color="#00ff00">One of the prisoners</font>
<font color="#00ff00">was wearing a mask.</font>

00:54.720 --> 00:56.800
<font color="#ffff00">Try to ensure he gets</font>
<font color="#ffff00">the rest he needs.</font>

00:58.440 --> 01:01.000
<font color="#ffffff">He's right. You need to rest.</font>

01:01.000 --> 01:02.480
<font color="#00ff00">Not yet.</font>

01:04.400 --> 01:05.440
<font color="#00ff00">Not yet.</font>

