03:14.120 --> 03:17.480
<font color="#00ffff">It is customary for the king's</font>
<font color="#00ffff">adversary to bow after the fight.</font>

03:18.640 --> 03:21.280
<font color="#ffff00">In Austria, it's customary</font>
<font color="#ffff00">for the loser to bow first.</font>

03:21.280 --> 03:24.200
<font color="#00ffff">This is not Austria, Your Majesty.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">This is Versailles.</font>

03:40.880 --> 03:44.480
<font color="#ffffff">A clever ploy. A vicious attack</font>
<font color="#ffffff">hidden behind a show of weakness.</font>

03:44.480 --> 03:47.400
<font color="#ffff00">History remembers the winner,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">not the manner of his victory.</font>

03:48.800 --> 03:50.560
<font color="#ffffff">On the subject of winners,</font>

03:50.560 --> 03:52.880
<font color="#ffffff">it is time for us</font>
<font color="#ffffff">to enter into negotiations.</font>

03:52.880 --> 03:55.920
<font color="#ffff00">Indeed. I received word</font>
<font color="#ffff00">from Rome this morning.</font>

03:55.920 --> 03:58.040
<font color="#ffff00">They look favourably</font>
<font color="#ffff00">on your guardianship</font>

03:58.040 --> 03:59.760
<font color="#ffff00">of Strasbourg and Luxembourg.</font>

03:59.760 --> 04:02.640
<font color="#ffffff">Excellent. Then it only remains</font>
<font color="#ffffff">for us to discuss Spain.</font>

04:02.640 --> 04:04.800
<font color="#ffff00">Is there so much to discuss?</font>

04:04.800 --> 04:07.200
<font color="#ffff00">Our claims are equal.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">We made a deal.</font>

04:07.200 --> 04:10.400
<font color="#ffff00">On King Charles' death, we split</font>
<font color="#ffff00">the spoils. Half to you, half to me.</font>

04:10.400 --> 04:13.200
<font color="#ffffff">Much has changed since that deal.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Such as?</font>

04:14.920 --> 04:16.600
<font color="#ffffff">I won the war.</font>

04:17.880 --> 04:19.640
<font color="#00ffff">May I ask who won?</font>

04:21.079 --> 04:24.480
<font color="#ffff00">His Majesty was kind enough</font>
<font color="#ffff00">to allow me victory.</font>

04:24.480 --> 04:26.320
<font color="#00ffff">His Majesty... </font><font color="#ffffff">It's nothing.</font>

04:28.480 --> 04:31.000
<font color="#ffffff">You seem...tired.</font>

04:31.000 --> 04:34.280
<font color="#00ffff">Nothing that can't be remedied</font>
<font color="#00ffff">by a walk in our gardens.</font>

04:45.120 --> 04:48.080
<font color="#ffff00">How much of Spain do you want?</font>

04:48.080 --> 04:49.120
<font color="#ffffff">All of it.</font>

05:06.240 --> 05:09.800
<font color="#ffffff">Brother,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">you really should be in bed.</font>

05:13.040 --> 05:15.800
<font color="#ffffff">I hear your imagination</font>
<font color="#ffffff">is playing games with you.</font>

05:15.800 --> 05:17.960
<font color="#00ff00">I was just explaining to His Majesty</font>

05:17.960 --> 05:20.280
<font color="#00ff00">that you had</font>
<font color="#00ff00">an unfortunate accident.</font>

05:20.280 --> 05:21.640
<font color="#ffff00">Accident?</font>

05:21.640 --> 05:23.920
<font color="#00ff00">I spoke with the governor</font>
<font color="#00ff00">and he assures me</font>

05:23.920 --> 05:25.640
<font color="#00ff00">His Highness slipped and fell.</font>

05:25.640 --> 05:27.440
<font color="#ffff00">Nonsense.</font>

05:27.440 --> 05:30.920
<font color="#ffff00">I went to the Bastille</font>
<font color="#ffff00">to see the prisoner.</font>

05:30.920 --> 05:33.000
<font color="#ffffff">The Duc de Sullun? </font><font color="#ffff00">Yes.</font>

05:34.960 --> 05:39.200
<font color="#ffff00">I went into his cell</font>
<font color="#ffff00">and I was struck and I fell.</font>

05:41.080 --> 05:43.600
<font color="#ffff00">He wore a mask made of iron.</font>

05:44.680 --> 05:47.280
<font color="#ffffff">I am told that the prisoner's</font>
<font color="#ffffff">real name is Macquart.</font>

05:49.760 --> 05:52.680
<font color="#ffff00">What? </font><font color="#00ff00">A petty criminal, deranged.</font>

05:52.680 --> 05:54.720
<font color="#00ff00">He believes himself to be a duke.</font>

05:54.720 --> 05:58.240
<font color="#00ff00">They gave him the title of</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Duc de Sullun to appease him.</font>

05:59.680 --> 06:02.880
<font color="#ffff00">Why Sullun?</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Have you forgotten your Latin?</font>

06:02.880 --> 06:06.400
<font color="#ffffff">Sullun is the inversion of nullus,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">meaning "no-one".</font>

06:06.400 --> 06:09.680
<font color="#ffff00">And the man in the iron mask?</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Does not exist.</font>

06:09.680 --> 06:11.600
<font color="#ffffff">It's all in your head.</font>

06:11.600 --> 06:14.280
<font color="#ffffff">Now, please, brother,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">go back to bed.</font>

06:49.320 --> 06:51.920
<font color="#00ffff">No. No. </font><font color="#ffff00">Why not?</font>
<font color="#00ffff">You'll soon be gone.</font>

06:51.920 --> 06:54.280
<font color="#ffff00">So let's enjoy each other's</font>
<font color="#ffff00">company while we can.</font>

06:54.280 --> 06:56.920
<font color="#00ffff">It will only increase</font>
<font color="#00ffff">the pain of your departure.</font>

07:03.240 --> 07:05.480
<font color="#ffff00">Can I trust you? </font><font color="#00ffff">Of course. Why?</font>

07:05.480 --> 07:07.680
<font color="#ffff00">I need your help. </font><font color="#00ffff">In what way?</font>

07:09.120 --> 07:11.840
<font color="#ffff00">Your husband is trying</font>
<font color="#ffff00">to destroy the dynasty</font>

07:11.840 --> 07:14.560
<font color="#ffff00">our ancestors have spent</font>
<font color="#ffff00">600 years creating.</font>

07:14.560 --> 07:17.400
<font color="#ffff00">He will claim all of Spain</font>
<font color="#ffff00">on your brother's death.</font>

07:17.400 --> 07:19.520
<font color="#ffff00">The Habsburgs will soon be extinct.</font>

07:20.760 --> 07:24.600
<font color="#00ffff">What do you intend to do about it?</font>
<font color="#ffff00">I will stop him. </font><font color="#00ffff">How?</font>

07:25.800 --> 07:29.120
<font color="#ffff00">My niece, Eleanor. She will</font>
<font color="#ffff00">marry your brother, Charles.</font>

07:29.120 --> 07:32.840
<font color="#ffff00">And I want you to write a letter to</font>
<font color="#ffff00">your brother recommending the union.</font>

07:32.840 --> 07:34.560
<font color="#00ffff">Why should I help you?</font>

07:36.400 --> 07:38.320
<font color="#ffff00">Because you're a Habsburg...</font>

07:39.760 --> 07:41.400
<font color="#ffff00">..just like me.</font>

07:42.680 --> 07:45.720
<font color="#ffff00">Because your husband has only ever</font>
<font color="#ffff00">seen you as a political tool.</font>

07:47.000 --> 07:49.520
<font color="#ffff00">He abandoned you the day</font>
<font color="#ffff00">he married you.</font>

07:49.520 --> 07:54.320
<font color="#ffff00">Since then, his only gifts to you</font>
<font color="#ffff00">have been solitude and infidelity.</font>

08:09.200 --> 08:10.960
<font color="#00ffff">"My dear brother Charles.</font>

08:13.600 --> 08:16.480
<font color="#00ffff">"I am writing to you</font>
<font color="#00ffff">concerning marriage."</font>

08:19.680 --> 08:21.480
<font color="#00ff00">They say that at Villarceaux</font>

08:21.480 --> 08:24.000
<font color="#00ff00">she spent her nights</font>
<font color="#00ff00">on her back in bliss</font>

08:24.000 --> 08:26.960
<font color="#00ff00">and her days on her knees</font>
<font color="#00ff00">in penance!</font>

08:26.960 --> 08:29.560
<font color="#00ff00">If you want my opinion,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">and I'm sure you do...</font>

08:33.080 --> 08:37.919
<font color="#00ff00">The question is, what colour for the</font>
<font color="#00ff00">forthcoming season? Blue or green?</font>

08:40.240 --> 08:42.400
<font color="#00ff00">Possibly a vexing proposition.</font>

08:45.560 --> 08:46.880
<font color="#00ffff">Duchesse.</font>

08:48.760 --> 08:51.720
<font color="#ffff00">She likes to parade herself</font>
<font color="#ffff00">as purer than the driven snow,</font>

08:51.720 --> 08:54.880
<font color="#ffff00">but behind that air of prudishness,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Madame is quite the slut.</font>

08:54.880 --> 08:57.200
<font color="#ffff00">And the next time I see the king,</font>

08:57.200 --> 08:59.800
<font color="#ffff00">I have a good mind</font>
<font color="#ffff00">to tell him about it!</font>

09:04.240 --> 09:07.120
<font color="#00ff00">Who are they talking about? </font><font color="#ffffff">Me.</font>

09:08.320 --> 09:11.120
<font color="#00ff00">But there's no truth to</font>
<font color="#00ff00">these rumours? </font><font color="#ffffff">Of course not.</font>

09:12.800 --> 09:14.680
<font color="#ffffff">If you will excuse me.</font>

09:43.280 --> 09:45.200
<font color="#ffff00">Her Ladyship seems upset.</font>

09:46.800 --> 09:48.560
<font color="#ffffff">Tell me, Bontemps.</font>

09:49.760 --> 09:52.120
<font color="#ffffff">Do you consider it</font>
<font color="#ffffff">the mark of nobility</font>

09:52.120 --> 09:55.160
<font color="#ffffff">to destroy a lady's reputation</font>
<font color="#ffffff">with sordid gossip and lies?</font>

09:56.960 --> 09:58.160
<font color="#ffff00">No.</font>

10:00.480 --> 10:02.120
<font color="#ffffff">Neither do I.</font>

10:27.720 --> 10:29.200
<font color="#ffffff">Madame de Montespan.</font>

10:31.000 --> 10:33.840
<font color="#00ffff">Good morning, Francoise.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Are you well?</font>

10:33.840 --> 10:36.520
<font color="#ffffff">It's you, isn't it?</font>
<font color="#00ffff">I beg your pardon?</font>

10:36.520 --> 10:39.840
<font color="#ffffff">Behind the rumours.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Why would I do such a thing?</font>

10:39.840 --> 10:41.920
<font color="#ffffff">Because you're jealous.</font>

10:41.920 --> 10:45.360
<font color="#00ffff">Of you? No, I think it is</font>
<font color="#00ffff">the other way round.</font>

10:45.360 --> 10:48.720
<font color="#00ffff">Because I was ready to risk</font>
<font color="#00ffff">everything and you are not.</font>

10:48.720 --> 10:51.240
<font color="#00ffff">Is it true you put other</font>
<font color="#00ffff">women in his bed?</font>

10:51.240 --> 10:54.280
<font color="#ffffff">The king has needs</font>
<font color="#ffffff">that must be satisfied.</font>

10:54.280 --> 10:56.200
<font color="#ffffff">These women mean nothing to him.</font>

10:56.200 --> 10:59.560
<font color="#00ffff">You're scared, aren't you?</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Of what? </font><font color="#00ffff">Of your own passion.</font>

11:00.760 --> 11:03.840
<font color="#00ffff">You're scared that if you give in</font>
<font color="#00ffff">to it, you will lose control.</font>

11:03.840 --> 11:06.280
<font color="#00ffff">You take refuge in piety and denial.</font>

11:06.280 --> 11:09.360
<font color="#00ffff">But behind the mask,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">you're just screaming with pain.</font>

11:19.240 --> 11:21.640
<font color="#ffffff">Any word from Spain?</font>
<font color="#ffff00">This morning, Sire.</font>

11:21.640 --> 11:24.360
<font color="#ffff00">King Charles is expecting</font>
<font color="#ffff00">our imminent arrival.</font>

11:24.360 --> 11:27.800
<font color="#ffffff">Inform him we shall leave as soon</font>
<font color="#ffffff">as our negotiations are concluded.</font>

11:27.800 --> 11:31.200
<font color="#ffff00">May I ask what approach</font>
<font color="#ffff00">His Majesty is considering?</font>

11:31.200 --> 11:33.040
<font color="#ffffff">The same as Louis' -</font>

11:33.040 --> 11:37.080
<font color="#ffffff">lie, haggle, concede,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">coerce, protest, and smile.</font>

11:38.120 --> 11:40.680
<font color="#ffff00">The king is dangerous.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">I advise His Majesty...</font>

11:40.680 --> 11:43.720
<font color="#ffffff">I don't need your advice.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">This is a game of cards.</font>

11:43.720 --> 11:47.400
<font color="#ffffff">The prize is Spain</font>
<font color="#ffffff">and I have the trump card.</font>

11:47.400 --> 11:48.440
<font color="#ffffff">Thank you.</font>

12:08.360 --> 12:10.440
<font color="#00ff00">There is talk in the salon.</font>

12:14.360 --> 12:16.280
<font color="#ffffff">I know.</font>

12:16.280 --> 12:19.280
<font color="#00ff00">Is there any truth in it? </font><font color="#ffffff">No, Sire.</font>

12:21.960 --> 12:25.000
<font color="#ffffff">It is scurrilous gossip</font>
<font color="#ffffff">designed to destroy my reputation.</font>

12:27.000 --> 12:28.280
<font color="#00ff00">And mine.</font>

12:30.440 --> 12:33.120
<font color="#ffffff">The king must know</font>
<font color="#ffffff">he has my total trust.</font>

12:35.400 --> 12:37.440
<font color="#ffffff">I only pray that I have his.</font>

12:41.920 --> 12:43.040
<font color="#00ff00">Come with me.</font>

12:47.040 --> 12:49.280
<font color="#00ffff">Uncle, may I go to the salon?</font>

12:49.280 --> 12:52.080
<font color="#ffffff">No. You'll stay here and</font>
<font color="#ffffff">practise your embroidery.</font>

12:52.080 --> 12:54.720
<font color="#00ffff">Embroidery is for spinsters.</font>

12:54.720 --> 12:56.000
<font color="#ffffff">Which is what you'll be</font>

12:56.000 --> 12:58.560
<font color="#ffffff">if you don't show a little</font>
<font color="#ffffff">more humility and respect.</font>

12:58.560 --> 13:01.720
<font color="#ffffff">And I want you to befriend</font>
<font color="#ffffff">the queen. </font><font color="#00ffff">Why?</font>

13:01.720 --> 13:03.240
<font color="#00ffff">She seems terribly dull to me.</font>

13:04.440 --> 13:07.760
<font color="#ffffff">She is a Habsburg, as are you.</font>

13:07.760 --> 13:10.160
<font color="#ffffff">Though she deserves</font>
<font color="#ffffff">that title more than you.</font>

13:10.160 --> 13:11.880
<font color="#00ffff">But what shall I talk to her about?</font>

13:11.880 --> 13:13.400
<font color="#ffffff">Spain.</font>

13:13.400 --> 13:15.160
<font color="#00ffff">Spain?</font>

13:15.160 --> 13:17.320
<font color="#ffffff">Its people, its culture,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">its traditions.</font>

13:17.320 --> 13:20.320
<font color="#00ffff">But I don't give a fig</font>
<font color="#00ffff">for culture and traditions.</font>

13:20.320 --> 13:23.280
<font color="#00ffff">I want fun.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">You are not here for fun.</font>

13:23.280 --> 13:26.760
<font color="#ffffff">You are here because I have</font>
<font color="#ffffff">a use for you. </font><font color="#00ffff">Yes, Uncle.</font>

13:30.560 --> 13:32.400
<font color="#ffff00">The king!</font>

13:50.240 --> 13:52.000
<font color="#ffffff">To lie is a sin.</font>

13:54.320 --> 13:56.720
<font color="#ffffff">To slander is a sin.</font>

13:58.360 --> 14:02.440
<font color="#ffffff">To seek to destroy someone</font>
<font color="#ffffff">through unfounded gossip is a sin.</font>

14:03.960 --> 14:07.520
<font color="#ffffff">A woman close to me who does</font>
<font color="#ffffff">great honour to this court</font>

14:07.520 --> 14:10.840
<font color="#ffffff">has seen her reputation</font>
<font color="#ffffff">stained by the poison of gossip.</font>

14:12.480 --> 14:14.920
<font color="#ffffff">In harming her, you harm your king.</font>

14:16.360 --> 14:18.000
<font color="#ffffff">This will stop...</font>

14:19.320 --> 14:20.640
<font color="#ffffff">..now.</font>

14:24.160 --> 14:26.160
<font color="#ffffff">Mademoiselle de Vasseur.</font>

14:26.160 --> 14:28.520
<font color="#ffffff">You are no longer</font>
<font color="#ffffff">welcome at Versailles.</font>

14:45.240 --> 14:47.040
<font color="#00ffff">How embarrassing!</font>

14:47.040 --> 14:48.800
<font color="#ffff00">I feel sorry for her.</font>

14:50.080 --> 14:53.240
<font color="#00ff00">That girl is innocent.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Nobody here is innocent.</font>

14:54.240 --> 14:56.400
<font color="#00ff00">You started those rumours.</font>

14:56.400 --> 14:58.440
<font color="#ffffff">They're not rumours, they're true.</font>

14:58.440 --> 15:01.880
<font color="#ffffff">She deserves to be punished</font>
<font color="#ffffff">for her past, just as I was.</font>

15:23.920 --> 15:26.720
<font color="#00ffff">I think you'd probably</font>
<font color="#00ffff">better arrest me.</font>

15:52.040 --> 15:54.520
<font color="#ffffff">I never thought I'd see you again.</font>

15:58.160 --> 16:00.480
<font color="#00ffff">Thought or hoped?</font>

16:00.480 --> 16:02.760
<font color="#ffffff">Where have you been? </font><font color="#00ffff">Holland.</font>

16:04.200 --> 16:06.680
<font color="#00ffff">I took refuge in the court</font>
<font color="#00ffff">of William of Orange.</font>

16:08.200 --> 16:10.160
<font color="#ffffff">What were you doing there?</font>

16:10.160 --> 16:12.160
<font color="#00ffff">That is where Thomas told me to go.</font>

16:13.320 --> 16:16.840
<font color="#00ffff">I was arrested, taken before</font>
<font color="#00ffff">the stadtholder and questioned.</font>

16:18.600 --> 16:21.320
<font color="#00ffff">They asked me all I knew</font>
<font color="#00ffff">about Versailles and the king,</font>

16:21.320 --> 16:24.000
<font color="#00ffff">and I told them all I knew,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">which is not very much.</font>

16:28.600 --> 16:30.000
<font color="#ffffff">And then?</font>

16:31.640 --> 16:34.640
<font color="#00ffff">He asked me whether</font>
<font color="#00ffff">I'd like to work for him...</font>

16:34.640 --> 16:35.680
<font color="#00ffff">..as a spy.</font>

16:37.320 --> 16:39.400
<font color="#ffffff">A spy. Here at Versailles.</font>

16:39.400 --> 16:42.520
<font color="#00ffff">Yes, Sire. I refused. </font><font color="#ffffff">Why?</font>

16:42.520 --> 16:44.840
<font color="#00ffff">Why would I serve a man</font>
<font color="#00ffff">who has already lost?</font>

16:44.840 --> 16:46.800
<font color="#ffffff">Is that what you told him? </font><font color="#00ffff">No.</font>

16:46.800 --> 16:48.840
<font color="#00ffff">I told him I was</font>
<font color="#00ffff">ill-suited for such work.</font>

16:48.840 --> 16:52.240
<font color="#ffffff">And he released you?</font>
<font color="#00ffff">No, Sire. I escaped.</font>

16:52.240 --> 16:55.440
<font color="#ffffff">How? </font><font color="#00ffff">The guard was</font>
<font color="#00ffff">susceptible to my charms.</font>

16:55.440 --> 16:59.120
<font color="#00ffff">I fled south, taking refuge in</font>
<font color="#00ffff">convents and taverns on the way.</font>

16:59.120 --> 17:02.440
<font color="#ffffff">And now you wish to reclaim</font>
<font color="#ffffff">your title and fortune?</font>

17:02.440 --> 17:04.760
<font color="#00ffff">I place myself at your mercy, Sire.</font>

17:06.920 --> 17:10.400
<font color="#ffffff">Bravo!</font>
<font color="#ffffff">On such a wonderful performance.</font>

17:10.400 --> 17:13.040
<font color="#00ffff">I speak the truth, Sire.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Lock her up.</font>

17:13.040 --> 17:15.440
<font color="#00ffff">Then His Majesty would</font>
<font color="#00ffff">not be interested to know</font>

17:15.440 --> 17:17.960
<font color="#00ffff">that William of Orange's army</font>
<font color="#00ffff">is on the march.</font>

17:17.960 --> 17:21.599
<font color="#00ffff">10,000 men are headed to Austria</font>
<font color="#00ffff">to support Emperor Leopold.</font>

17:23.119 --> 17:26.440
<font color="#ffffff">How do you know this?</font>
<font color="#00ffff">General de Salm told me.</font>

17:26.440 --> 17:28.520
<font color="#ffffff">Another who was susceptible</font>
<font color="#ffffff">to your charms?</font>

17:28.520 --> 17:30.600
<font color="#00ffff">Why would I tell</font>
<font color="#00ffff">His Majesty such a thing</font>

17:30.600 --> 17:33.000
<font color="#00ffff">if I was a spy for</font>
<font color="#00ffff">William of Orange?</font>

17:35.480 --> 17:38.120
<font color="#ffff00">I shall make a few inquiries</font>
<font color="#ffff00">to confirm her story.</font>

17:39.480 --> 17:42.640
<font color="#ffff00">In the meantime,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">she will remain under lock and key.</font>

17:42.640 --> 17:43.880
<font color="#ffffff">Very well.</font>

18:08.480 --> 18:11.920
<font color="#00ff00">Your Highness, the doctor was most</font>
<font color="#00ff00">insistent that your remain in bed.</font>

18:11.920 --> 18:13.760
<font color="#ffffff">He is no longer my doctor.</font>

18:13.760 --> 18:15.520
<font color="#ffffff">And I know what I saw.</font>

18:26.440 --> 18:28.320
<font color="#00ff00">Go to the stables.</font>

18:28.320 --> 18:31.240
<font color="#00ff00">Tell Monsieur Jadot to prepare</font>
<font color="#00ff00">a horse and a messenger</font>

18:31.240 --> 18:33.080
<font color="#00ff00">leaving immediately for Rome.</font>

18:37.400 --> 18:39.160
<font color="#ffffff">Dios mejora las horas.</font>

18:39.160 --> 18:41.200
<font color="#ffff00">Dios mejora las horas.</font>

18:42.640 --> 18:44.000
<font color="#ffff00">What does it mean?</font>

18:45.520 --> 18:47.640
<font color="#ffffff">You would say,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">"After rain comes sun".</font>

18:47.640 --> 18:50.040
<font color="#ffff00">It's beautiful.</font>

18:50.040 --> 18:52.000
<font color="#ffff00">And what do the Spanish eat?</font>

18:52.000 --> 18:55.240
<font color="#ffffff">Well, the king's favourite dish</font>
<font color="#ffffff">is rabo de toro.</font>

18:55.240 --> 18:57.080
<font color="#ffff00">What's that?</font>

18:57.080 --> 19:01.200
<font color="#ffffff">It's a stew made from the tails</font>
<font color="#ffffff">of bulls killed by a matador.</font>

19:05.960 --> 19:10.040
<font color="#ffff00">And the king, your brother,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">you must miss him?</font>

19:11.640 --> 19:15.120
<font color="#ffffff">Yes. I miss him terribly.</font>

19:15.120 --> 19:17.480
<font color="#ffffff">But I have his portrait here</font>
<font color="#ffffff">to remind me of him.</font>

19:28.840 --> 19:31.600
<font color="#ffffff">It's not his fault</font>
<font color="#ffffff">he was born that way.</font>

19:33.000 --> 19:35.960
<font color="#ffffff">As you can imagine, he suffers.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">But he has a noble heart.</font>

19:40.480 --> 19:43.200
<font color="#ffff00">If you claim all of Spain</font>
<font color="#ffff00">and its territories,</font>

19:43.200 --> 19:45.720
<font color="#ffff00">you will trigger a war</font>
<font color="#ffff00">with every country in Europe.</font>

19:45.720 --> 19:48.720
<font color="#ffffff">I have just won one war and my army</font>
<font color="#ffffff">is well-prepared for another.</font>

19:48.720 --> 19:50.720
<font color="#ffff00">This would not be a war</font>
<font color="#ffff00">you could win, Louis.</font>

19:50.720 --> 19:52.840
<font color="#ffff00">It would be a war without end.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Is that what you want?</font>

19:52.840 --> 19:56.360
<font color="#ffffff">I want what is mine.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">You think everything's yours.</font>

19:56.360 --> 19:59.240
<font color="#ffffff">What will you do if</font>
<font color="#ffffff">the Turks advance on Vienna?</font>

19:59.240 --> 20:01.200
<font color="#ffffff">Hope it rains?</font>

20:01.200 --> 20:04.520
<font color="#ffffff">Or are you counting on the rabble</font>
<font color="#ffffff">that is William of Orange's army?</font>

20:07.080 --> 20:11.200
<font color="#ffffff">The only person who can</font>
<font color="#ffffff">protect you is me.</font>

20:11.200 --> 20:14.160
<font color="#ffff00">You already have</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Luxembourg and Strasbourg</font>

20:14.160 --> 20:15.680
<font color="#ffff00">in return for your protection.</font>

20:15.680 --> 20:18.480
<font color="#ffffff">And I want Spain.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">The Pope would never approve it.</font>

20:18.480 --> 20:21.040
<font color="#ffff00">Not even you would</font>
<font color="#ffff00">challenge the Pope.</font>

20:21.040 --> 20:23.520
<font color="#ffffff">I'll settle on 80%.</font>

20:23.520 --> 20:26.160
<font color="#ffff00">My dear cousin, you know perfectly</font>
<font color="#ffff00">well that is still too much</font>

20:26.160 --> 20:28.040
<font color="#ffff00">and I cannot give in</font>
<font color="#ffff00">to your demands.</font>

20:28.040 --> 20:30.720
<font color="#ffffff">Then you'd better start</font>
<font color="#ffffff">taking Turkish lessons.</font>

20:51.400 --> 20:53.760
<font color="#00ffff">I trust Your Highness</font>
<font color="#00ffff">is fully recovered.</font>

20:55.680 --> 21:00.440
<font color="#ffffff">What's going on? </font><font color="#00ffff">Nothing,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Your Highness. It's just...</font>

21:00.440 --> 21:02.120
<font color="#00ffff">..an accident.</font>

21:08.720 --> 21:10.920
<font color="#00ffff">Cut his wrists, poor wretch.</font>

21:14.960 --> 21:16.880
<font color="#ffffff">His name? </font><font color="#00ffff">Macquart.</font>

21:19.840 --> 21:21.720
<font color="#ffffff">Why did he take his own life?</font>

21:21.720 --> 21:25.240
<font color="#00ffff">Would His Highness wish to spend</font>
<font color="#00ffff">the rest of his days in here?</font>

21:39.520 --> 21:41.880
<font color="#ffffff">Who struck me? </font><font color="#00ffff">Your Highness?</font>

21:44.640 --> 21:46.680
<font color="#ffffff">Don't play games with me.</font>

21:46.680 --> 21:50.200
<font color="#00ffff">His Highness slipped</font>
<font color="#00ffff">and hit his head on the floor.</font>

21:50.200 --> 21:51.480
<font color="#00ffff">I witnessed it myself.</font>

21:51.480 --> 21:54.520
<font color="#ffffff">The last time I saw this man,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">he wore a mask made of iron.</font>

21:54.520 --> 21:57.520
<font color="#00ffff">Your Highness, there is no prisoner</font>
<font color="#00ffff">wearing such a thing.</font>

21:57.520 --> 21:59.600
<font color="#00ffff">I would know if there was.</font>

22:04.520 --> 22:06.160
<font color="#00ffff">Take him away now.</font>

22:35.560 --> 22:39.320
<font color="#00ff00">Daddy's lying down</font>
<font color="#00ff00">for a sleep in the hay.</font>

22:39.320 --> 22:42.520
<font color="#00ff00">Along come a snake</font>
<font color="#00ff00">and he winks at the sow.</font>

22:43.960 --> 22:48.240
<font color="#00ff00">She lies on her back</font>
<font color="#00ff00">and says, "Give it to me now."</font>

22:48.240 --> 22:49.960
<font color="#00ff00">Poor bloody fool.</font>

22:55.560 --> 22:57.080
<font color="#ffffff">Do you know who I am?</font>

22:57.080 --> 22:59.160
<font color="#00ff00">I know you better</font>
<font color="#00ff00">than you know yourself.</font>

23:00.560 --> 23:03.120
<font color="#00ff00">Philippe of</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Gutter, Arsewipe and Goat Dung.</font>

23:06.600 --> 23:08.560
<font color="#ffffff">Did you know the man in that cell?</font>

23:09.840 --> 23:12.400
<font color="#ffffff">Duc du Sullun. Macquart.</font>

23:12.400 --> 23:15.560
<font color="#00ff00">Everybody knows him. Nobody</font>
<font color="#00ff00">knows him. Know what I'm saying?</font>

23:17.480 --> 23:22.440
<font color="#ffffff">Who was he? </font><font color="#00ff00">Don't look him</font>
<font color="#00ff00">in the eyes. He'll eat you up.</font>

23:22.440 --> 23:24.080
<font color="#ffffff">Is he still alive?</font>

23:24.080 --> 23:26.560
<font color="#00ff00">He's undead. You can't kill him!</font>

23:26.560 --> 23:29.920
<font color="#ffffff">Did he wear a mask?</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Poor bugger. </font><font color="#ffffff">Did he wear a mask?!</font>

23:29.920 --> 23:32.600
<font color="#00ff00">He'll kill you with his eyes.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Shut up!</font>

23:34.000 --> 23:35.600
<font color="#00ff00">Cain, brother of Abel.</font>

23:36.760 --> 23:40.320
<font color="#00ff00">Two brothers drenched in blood</font>
<font color="#00ff00">and cursed forever!</font>

23:41.800 --> 23:43.600
<font color="#ffffff">ECHOING: </font><font color="#00ff00">Cain, brother of Abel.</font>

23:48.760 --> 23:51.360
<font color="#ffffff">Good morning.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Good morning, Your Highness.</font>

23:53.120 --> 23:54.560
<font color="#ffff00">May I?</font>

23:58.400 --> 24:00.480
<font color="#ffff00">He's beautiful.</font>

24:00.480 --> 24:02.200
<font color="#ffffff">Thank you.</font>

24:03.360 --> 24:05.360
<font color="#00ffff">Your Highness, if I may.</font>

24:05.360 --> 24:07.120
<font color="#00ffff">I don't mean to seem impertinent,</font>

24:07.120 --> 24:10.520
<font color="#00ffff">but I think you are making</font>
<font color="#00ffff">a grave mistake by keeping him here.</font>

24:11.800 --> 24:15.320
<font color="#ffff00">Is that so? </font><font color="#00ffff">Well, it is not</font>
<font color="#00ffff">the right environment for a child.</font>

24:15.320 --> 24:16.880
<font color="#ffff00">May I ask,</font>

24:16.880 --> 24:19.360
<font color="#ffff00">what gives you the right to tell me</font>
<font color="#ffff00">how to look after my child?</font>

24:19.360 --> 24:24.200
<font color="#00ffff">I was a governess.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Yet never a mother. </font><font color="#00ffff">Alas, no.</font>

24:24.200 --> 24:27.360
<font color="#ffff00">You'd think one of your many lovers</font>
<font color="#ffff00">would have solved that problem.</font>

24:28.920 --> 24:30.440
<font color="#00ffff">It would seem your reputation</font>

24:30.440 --> 24:32.680
<font color="#00ffff">for honesty and integrity</font>
<font color="#00ffff">is ill-deserved.</font>

24:36.680 --> 24:38.720
<font color="#ffffff">Well, that went well.</font>

24:42.720 --> 24:45.680
<font color="#ffff00">You're sure there is</font>
<font color="#ffff00">no error in the calculations?</font>

24:45.680 --> 24:47.240
<font color="#00ff00">I'm certain, Sire.</font>

24:47.240 --> 24:50.400
<font color="#00ff00">The money required to finance</font>
<font color="#00ff00">our expansion into the Americas</font>

24:50.400 --> 24:52.280
<font color="#00ff00">and the fortification of our borders</font>

24:52.280 --> 24:54.560
<font color="#00ff00">will add another two million</font>
<font color="#00ff00">to the deficit.</font>

24:54.560 --> 24:56.440
<font color="#ffff00">What of the new taxes?</font>

24:56.440 --> 24:59.320
<font color="#00ff00">In place, Sire, but the people</font>
<font color="#00ff00">are refusing to pay them.</font>

24:59.320 --> 25:02.280
<font color="#ffff00">The people of France must learn</font>
<font color="#ffff00">to respect and obey the law.</font>

25:02.280 --> 25:03.720
<font color="#00ff00">But, Sire...</font>

25:05.160 --> 25:06.840
<font color="#00ff00">..how on earth...?</font>

25:06.840 --> 25:08.360
<font color="#ffff00">Inspire them.</font>

25:13.920 --> 25:17.880
<font color="#ffff00">Yes? </font><font color="#00ffff">Sire, the rumours</font>
<font color="#00ffff">regarding Madame de Maintenon.</font>

25:17.880 --> 25:20.280
<font color="#00ffff">I've discovered their source.</font>

25:20.280 --> 25:21.440
<font color="#ffff00">Who was it?</font>

25:25.360 --> 25:26.760
<font color="#ffff00">Bring her to me.</font>

25:39.760 --> 25:43.200
<font color="#ffffff">We cannot allow this.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">It could damage the business.</font>

25:43.200 --> 25:45.520
<font color="#ffff00">It's not their fault</font>
<font color="#ffff00">if they can't pay.</font>

25:45.520 --> 25:47.880
<font color="#ffffff">Of course they can pay.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">They just don't want to.</font>

25:50.520 --> 25:52.680
<font color="#ffffff">Tell me.</font>

25:52.680 --> 25:55.520
<font color="#ffffff">Who here has not paid their taxes?</font>

25:55.520 --> 25:56.640
<font color="#ffffff">Raise your hand.</font>

26:05.360 --> 26:07.560
<font color="#ffffff">You would disobey your king?</font>

26:07.560 --> 26:11.480
<font color="#00ffff">I have always paid my taxes,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">but not these.</font>

26:11.480 --> 26:13.040
<font color="#00ffff">The king's gone too far.</font>

26:13.040 --> 26:15.240
<font color="#ffffff">The taxes are for the common good.</font>

26:15.240 --> 26:18.160
<font color="#00ffff">I tell you what. If you want us to</font>
<font color="#00ffff">pay our taxes, give us more money.</font>

26:18.160 --> 26:19.400
<font color="#ffffff">If I pay you more money,</font>

26:19.400 --> 26:22.000
<font color="#ffffff">the business will fold</font>
<font color="#ffffff">and you'll be out of work.</font>

26:22.000 --> 26:23.560
<font color="#00ffff">Whether we work or not,</font>

26:23.560 --> 26:26.840
<font color="#00ffff">most of us are going to die</font>
<font color="#00ffff">in rags and poverty.</font>

26:26.840 --> 26:29.000
<font color="#00ffff">Will Louis the Great shed a tear?</font>

26:30.480 --> 26:31.800
<font color="#ffff00">Come.</font>

27:08.880 --> 27:11.360
<font color="#00ff00">There is a piece of paper</font>
<font color="#00ff00">on the table.</font>

27:11.360 --> 27:14.000
<font color="#00ff00">You will read it aloud</font>
<font color="#00ff00">and then sign it.</font>

27:19.480 --> 27:24.560
<font color="#ffff00">"I, the Marquise de Montespan,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">do hereby renounce</font>

27:24.560 --> 27:27.480
<font color="#ffff00">"and relinquish my place</font>
<font color="#ffff00">at the court of Versailles.</font>

27:29.920 --> 27:33.440
<font color="#ffff00">"I pledge to sever all contact</font>
<font color="#ffff00">with anyone I may know at the palace</font>

27:33.440 --> 27:36.240
<font color="#ffff00">"and will take no further</font>
<font color="#ffff00">part in court life.</font>

27:38.080 --> 27:41.920
<font color="#ffff00">"I shall devote the rest of my days</font>
<font color="#ffff00">to prayer and charitable works.</font>

27:44.440 --> 27:47.040
<font color="#ffff00">"I have sinned,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">and I accept my penance."</font>

27:49.680 --> 27:52.200
<font color="#00ff00">Your affairs have all been prepared.</font>

27:52.200 --> 27:56.880
<font color="#00ff00">A carriage will take you immediately</font>
<font color="#00ff00">to the Convent of St Ursule.</font>

27:58.240 --> 28:00.240
<font color="#00ff00">You will never return here.</font>

28:02.360 --> 28:05.120
<font color="#ffff00">The condemned normally</font>
<font color="#ffff00">has a right to a last word</font>

28:05.120 --> 28:06.840
<font color="#ffff00">before being led away.</font>

28:15.800 --> 28:19.720
<font color="#ffff00">Where I once saw</font>
<font color="#ffff00">the warm face of a man,</font>

28:19.720 --> 28:22.040
<font color="#ffff00">I now see</font>
<font color="#ffff00">the stone face of a tyrant.</font>

28:23.800 --> 28:26.000
<font color="#ffff00">You treat those around you</font>
<font color="#ffff00">like slaves</font>

28:26.000 --> 28:28.360
<font color="#ffff00">and you place yourself</font>
<font color="#ffff00">beyond mortal sway.</font>

28:29.720 --> 28:31.440
<font color="#ffff00">But remember the story of Icarus.</font>

28:32.920 --> 28:36.520
<font color="#ffff00">Fly too close to the sun</font>
<font color="#ffff00">and you will fall and drown.</font>

28:44.200 --> 28:45.240
<font color="#ffffff">The dance is over.</font>

28:47.120 --> 28:48.280
<font color="#ffffff">Go.</font>

28:56.480 --> 28:57.920
<font color="#ffffff">DOOR CLOSES</font>

28:59.840 --> 29:01.360
<font color="#ffffff">In time I will forgive her.</font>

29:02.720 --> 29:04.760
<font color="#ffffff">But I will never forget.</font>

30:17.160 --> 30:18.480
<font color="#ffff00">Sire!</font>

30:22.360 --> 30:24.840
<font color="#ffffff">I apologise. Had I known...</font>

30:24.840 --> 30:27.160
<font color="#ffff00">How long have you been there?</font>

30:27.160 --> 30:29.240
<font color="#ffffff">Let me get you a...</font>

30:39.640 --> 30:41.160
<font color="#ffff00">Thank you.</font>

30:45.880 --> 30:49.320
<font color="#ffff00">I wanted to thank you for</font>
<font color="#ffff00">what you said in the salon today.</font>

30:51.840 --> 30:53.400
<font color="#ffff00">You defended my honour.</font>

30:54.840 --> 30:56.760
<font color="#ffffff">I was honoured to do so.</font>

31:11.680 --> 31:13.120
<font color="#ffff00">Please stop.</font>

31:14.600 --> 31:16.040
<font color="#ffff00">I can't.</font>

31:17.640 --> 31:20.840
<font color="#ffffff">Why not?</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Don't tell me you don't want to.</font>

31:31.040 --> 31:33.040
<font color="#ffff00">Enough.</font>

31:33.040 --> 31:35.600
<font color="#ffff00">His Majesty takes advantage</font>
<font color="#ffff00">of his station.</font>

31:35.600 --> 31:38.240
<font color="#ffffff">Sometimes, I don't know</font>
<font color="#ffffff">what my station is with you.</font>

31:39.280 --> 31:41.240
<font color="#ffff00">I would ask you to leave.</font>

31:45.800 --> 31:46.880
<font color="#ffff00">Sire?</font>

31:51.240 --> 31:54.200
<font color="#ffff00">The Marquise de Canchy</font>
<font color="#ffff00">awaits His Majesty in his room.</font>

33:02.960 --> 33:04.760
<font color="#ffff00">I thought you weren't going to come.</font>

33:04.760 --> 33:06.360
<font color="#ffffff">I've changed my mind ten times.</font>

33:09.680 --> 33:12.000
<font color="#ffff00">Did you write the letter? </font><font color="#ffffff">Yes.</font>

33:36.520 --> 33:38.640
<font color="#00ff00">Good morning, Sire.</font>

33:39.880 --> 33:42.480
<font color="#00ff00">I trust you passed</font>
<font color="#00ff00">a satisfactory night.</font>

33:44.800 --> 33:46.200
<font color="#ffffff">Come join me a moment.</font>

34:03.240 --> 34:05.360
<font color="#00ff00">Something amuses His Majesty?</font>

34:09.120 --> 34:11.360
<font color="#ffffff">Everyone looks at a king and says,</font>

34:11.360 --> 34:14.040
<font color="#ffffff">"I would give anything</font>
<font color="#ffffff">to be in his place.</font>

34:14.040 --> 34:16.080
<font color="#ffffff">"All he wants is his."</font>

34:18.840 --> 34:20.880
<font color="#ffffff">But they see only the surface.</font>

34:22.360 --> 34:24.960
<font color="#ffffff">They see nothing of</font>
<font color="#ffffff">the shadows below.</font>

34:27.520 --> 34:29.880
<font color="#00ff00">No-one has all he wants, Sire.</font>

34:31.520 --> 34:33.400
<font color="#00ff00">Not even a king.</font>

34:41.679 --> 34:42.960
<font color="#ffffff">Look.</font>

34:49.080 --> 34:52.600
<font color="#ffffff">From the darkest shadow</font>
<font color="#ffffff">springs the brightest light.</font>

35:13.160 --> 35:15.720
<font color="#ffff00">You've come to torture me?</font>

35:15.720 --> 35:19.600
<font color="#00ffff">My men have checked every detail</font>
<font color="#00ffff">of your journey from Holland.</font>

35:21.400 --> 35:23.920
<font color="#00ffff">It seems you were telling the truth.</font>

35:23.920 --> 35:25.920
<font color="#ffff00">You sound almost disappointed.</font>

35:27.600 --> 35:30.200
<font color="#00ffff">The king has given permission</font>
<font color="#00ffff">for your release.</font>

35:36.600 --> 35:39.320
<font color="#00ffff">You are once again</font>
<font color="#00ffff">the Duchesse de Cassel.</font>

35:40.440 --> 35:43.320
<font color="#ffff00">You still don't trust me, do you?</font>

35:43.320 --> 35:45.200
<font color="#00ffff">No.</font>

35:45.200 --> 35:46.680
<font color="#00ffff">You may be free...</font>

35:48.200 --> 35:52.440
<font color="#00ffff">..but whatever you do, whoever</font>
<font color="#00ffff">you talk to, wherever you go...</font>

35:55.080 --> 35:57.160
<font color="#00ffff">..I'll be watching you.</font>

36:01.640 --> 36:04.000
<font color="#ffff00">Even when I retire to my chambers?</font>

36:10.200 --> 36:11.720
<font color="#00ff00">Give me a smile.</font>

36:15.200 --> 36:17.040
<font color="#00ff00">OK. There.</font>

36:18.160 --> 36:19.560
<font color="#00ff00">That's it.</font>

36:21.200 --> 36:23.520
<font color="#00ff00">Philippe, he smiled.</font>

36:23.520 --> 36:26.640
<font color="#00ff00">Come and look.</font>
<font color="#00ff00">He's simply adorable.</font>

36:26.640 --> 36:30.760
<font color="#00ff00">Look at those blue eyes.</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Aren't they beautiful?</font>

36:30.760 --> 36:32.520
<font color="#ffffff">What did you say?</font>

36:32.520 --> 36:34.920
<font color="#00ff00">I said, look at those blue eyes.</font>

36:44.240 --> 36:46.240
<font color="#00ff00">Where are you going now?</font>

36:47.840 --> 36:49.560
<font color="#ffffff">DOOR SLAMS</font>

36:49.560 --> 36:51.440
<font color="#ffffff">BABY CRIES</font>

36:55.240 --> 36:56.760
<font color="#00ffff">Your Highness.</font>

36:56.760 --> 37:01.000
<font color="#ffffff">Does the name Macquart mean</font>
<font color="#ffffff">anything to you? </font><font color="#00ffff">No. Should it?</font>

37:01.000 --> 37:02.680
<font color="#ffffff">Probably not.</font>

37:02.680 --> 37:05.080
<font color="#ffffff">A thief held in the Bastille.</font>

37:05.080 --> 37:07.280
<font color="#ffffff">When I saw him for the first time...</font>

37:08.760 --> 37:11.560
<font color="#ffffff">..his face was hidden</font>
<font color="#ffffff">behind an iron mask.</font>

37:11.560 --> 37:14.280
<font color="#ffffff">When I went again</font>
<font color="#ffffff">to the prison yesterday,</font>

37:14.280 --> 37:16.600
<font color="#ffffff">they were removing a dead</font>
<font color="#ffffff">body from his cell.</font>

37:17.960 --> 37:20.560
<font color="#00ffff">Macquart? </font><font color="#ffffff">That's what</font>
<font color="#ffffff">someone wants me to believe.</font>

37:21.560 --> 37:25.120
<font color="#ffffff">He wore the same clothes</font>
<font color="#ffffff">and was of similar size.</font>

37:25.120 --> 37:27.680
<font color="#ffffff">But the first man</font>
<font color="#ffffff">I saw had blue eyes.</font>

37:28.720 --> 37:30.720
<font color="#ffffff">The man yesterday had brown eyes.</font>

37:32.040 --> 37:34.840
<font color="#00ffff">And why has His Highness</font>
<font color="#00ffff">approached me on this matter?</font>

37:34.840 --> 37:38.720
<font color="#ffffff">Because I want you to help me get</font>
<font color="#ffffff">to the bottom of this. </font><font color="#00ffff">I'd like to.</font>

37:39.920 --> 37:43.120
<font color="#00ffff">However... </font><font color="#ffffff">You only serve the king.</font>

37:43.120 --> 37:44.160
<font color="#00ffff">Precisely.</font>

37:46.240 --> 37:48.120
<font color="#ffffff">Then don't see this as work.</font>

37:49.120 --> 37:51.480
<font color="#ffffff">See this more as a leisure activity.</font>

37:54.240 --> 37:56.920
<font color="#ffffff">I know you're intrigued.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">I can see it in your eyes.</font>

38:01.760 --> 38:03.560
<font color="#00ffff">Length, nine inches.</font>

38:05.320 --> 38:07.520
<font color="#00ffff">Arch, three and nine.</font>

38:16.440 --> 38:19.640
<font color="#ffffff">Tell me about the mood</font>
<font color="#ffffff">of the people in Paris.</font>

38:19.640 --> 38:21.240
<font color="#00ffff">They are happy, Sire...</font>

38:22.200 --> 38:24.640
<font color="#00ffff">..to be ruled by</font>
<font color="#00ffff">so generous a monarch.</font>

38:24.640 --> 38:26.120
<font color="#ffffff">Yet life is hard for them.</font>

38:26.120 --> 38:28.840
<font color="#ffffff">I understand they are unhappy</font>
<font color="#ffffff">about paying their taxes.</font>

38:28.840 --> 38:31.680
<font color="#00ffff">Nothing that is not cured</font>
<font color="#00ffff">by hard work, Sire.</font>

38:31.680 --> 38:34.520
<font color="#ffffff">But I'm sure there must be</font>
<font color="#ffffff">some who despise their king.</font>

38:35.760 --> 38:38.320
<font color="#00ffff">There will always be those, Sire.</font>

38:38.320 --> 38:40.480
<font color="#00ffff">They do not see the glory of France.</font>

38:40.480 --> 38:42.240
<font color="#00ffff">They think only of themselves.</font>

38:42.240 --> 38:43.880
<font color="#ffff00">They are hungry.</font>

38:43.880 --> 38:45.960
<font color="#00ff00">Mind your tongue.</font>

38:45.960 --> 38:47.520
<font color="#ffffff">It's quite all right.</font>

38:49.120 --> 38:51.120
<font color="#ffffff">I'm rather enjoying this discussion.</font>

38:52.840 --> 38:55.120
<font color="#ffffff">You must understand that</font>
<font color="#ffffff">a king is only there</font>

38:55.120 --> 38:57.360
<font color="#ffffff">to serve his people and his country.</font>

38:57.360 --> 39:00.000
<font color="#ffffff">To defend the land,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">to develop trade and commerce,</font>

39:00.000 --> 39:01.680
<font color="#ffffff">to pay for construction.</font>

39:01.680 --> 39:03.680
<font color="#ffffff">All these things require money</font>

39:03.680 --> 39:07.200
<font color="#ffffff">and the only way to raise money</font>
<font color="#ffffff">is through taxation.</font>

39:07.200 --> 39:08.800
<font color="#ffffff">Is that so wrong?</font>

39:10.040 --> 39:12.000
<font color="#ffff00">It is...</font>

39:12.000 --> 39:13.880
<font color="#ffff00">..if it bleeds the people dry.</font>

39:15.200 --> 39:17.600
<font color="#ffff00">The people His Majesty</font>
<font color="#ffff00">claims to serve...</font>

39:19.000 --> 39:21.880
<font color="#ffff00">..believe he serves</font>
<font color="#ffff00">only personal ambitions.</font>

39:21.880 --> 39:23.320
<font color="#00ffff">What my sister meant to say is</font>

39:23.320 --> 39:25.560
<font color="#00ffff">there are certain greedy</font>
<font color="#00ffff">and selfish people.</font>

39:25.560 --> 39:27.920
<font color="#ffff00">No. What I meant to say</font>
<font color="#ffff00">is what I said.</font>

39:33.360 --> 39:34.960
<font color="#ffffff">But you are wrong.</font>

39:34.960 --> 39:38.520
<font color="#ffffff">I do not seek glory for myself,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">but for France.</font>

39:38.520 --> 39:41.760
<font color="#ffff00">Your people care little for</font>
<font color="#ffff00">the glory of France, Sire.</font>

39:41.760 --> 39:45.240
<font color="#ffff00">They are grateful for</font>
<font color="#ffff00">clean water and lighting,</font>

39:45.240 --> 39:47.640
<font color="#ffff00">but neither will</font>
<font color="#ffff00">fill their stomachs.</font>

39:57.360 --> 39:59.320
<font color="#ffffff">I thank you for your honesty.</font>

40:06.240 --> 40:08.480
<font color="#00ffff">Have you lost your mind?</font>

40:08.480 --> 40:10.840
<font color="#ffff00">Have you forgotten your origins?</font>

40:10.840 --> 40:13.720
<font color="#ffff00">You used to be a friend of</font>
<font color="#ffff00">the people. Now you've turned into</font>

40:13.720 --> 40:16.560
<font color="#ffff00">exactly the sort of money-grabbing</font>
<font color="#ffff00">coward you used to despise.</font>

40:16.560 --> 40:19.880
<font color="#00ffff">The king has bestowed great honour</font>
<font color="#00ffff">on our family and our business,</font>

40:19.880 --> 40:22.040
<font color="#00ffff">and you just threw it</font>
<font color="#00ffff">back in his face.</font>

40:22.040 --> 40:24.520
<font color="#ffff00">He asked me what I thought</font>
<font color="#ffff00">and I told him.</font>

40:24.520 --> 40:27.160
<font color="#ffff00">Would you have me lie? </font><font color="#00ffff">Yes. </font><font color="#ffff00">Why?</font>

40:27.160 --> 40:28.880
<font color="#00ffff">Because he's the king!</font>

40:28.880 --> 40:31.120
<font color="#ffff00">And one should always</font>
<font color="#ffff00">lie to the king?</font>

40:40.320 --> 40:43.000
<font color="#ffff00">Your Highness. </font><font color="#ffffff">You have news?</font>

40:46.520 --> 40:49.160
<font color="#ffff00">I've spoken to my agents in Paris.</font>

40:49.160 --> 40:52.280
<font color="#ffff00">It appears that Macquart</font>
<font color="#ffff00">was well-known to the police.</font>

40:52.280 --> 40:55.080
<font color="#ffff00">Ten counts of petty theft,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">two of extortion.</font>

40:55.080 --> 41:01.040
<font color="#ffff00">But, by and large, a harmless fellow</font>
<font color="#ffff00">simply trying to feed his family.</font>

41:01.040 --> 41:04.480
<font color="#ffffff">So if he was just a petty criminal,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">what was he doing in the Bastille?</font>

41:06.960 --> 41:08.880
<font color="#ffff00">He was not in the Bastille.</font>

41:10.280 --> 41:12.400
<font color="#ffff00">He was imprisoned in Clichy.</font>

41:12.400 --> 41:15.800
<font color="#ffff00">Someone must have moved him</font>
<font color="#ffff00">to the Bastille.</font>

41:21.760 --> 41:24.520
<font color="#00ffff">And the Pope promises to look</font>
<font color="#00ffff">favourably on the match?</font>

41:24.520 --> 41:25.960
<font color="#00ff00">Yes, Your Majesty.</font>

41:25.960 --> 41:29.080
<font color="#00ff00">His concern is that the balance</font>
<font color="#00ff00">of power is maintained.</font>

41:29.080 --> 41:32.480
<font color="#00ff00">If Louis acquires Spain</font>
<font color="#00ff00">then all of Europe will follow.</font>

41:33.720 --> 41:35.560
<font color="#00ffff">He needn't worry about that.</font>

41:39.200 --> 41:42.160
<font color="#00ffff">Louis, I have good news and bad.</font>

41:43.440 --> 41:44.800
<font color="#ffffff">The good?</font>

41:44.800 --> 41:46.680
<font color="#00ffff">I have examined all the options</font>

41:46.680 --> 41:49.360
<font color="#00ffff">and have concluded that</font>
<font color="#00ffff">your proposal to take 80%</font>

41:49.360 --> 41:52.800
<font color="#00ffff">of Spain and its possessions</font>
<font color="#00ffff">on Charles's death is the best.</font>

41:52.800 --> 41:56.080
<font color="#ffffff">Your generosity surprises me.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">There's nothing generous about it.</font>

41:56.080 --> 41:58.640
<font color="#00ffff">I've had enough of war.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">My army is exhausted.</font>

41:58.640 --> 42:01.520
<font color="#00ffff">My people are broken.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">They want peace and stability.</font>

42:01.520 --> 42:04.360
<font color="#00ffff">I believe this to be the</font>
<font color="#00ffff">best way to give them that.</font>

42:05.560 --> 42:07.040
<font color="#ffffff">And the bad news?</font>

42:07.040 --> 42:09.360
<font color="#00ffff">I must leave you. My people need me.</font>

42:10.720 --> 42:14.400
<font color="#ffffff">You will be missed.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Come. Let's embrace.</font>

42:14.400 --> 42:16.360
<font color="#ffffff">As cousins and as allies.</font>

42:16.360 --> 42:19.520
<font color="#00ffff">Tomorrow I will return to Vienna.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Of course.</font>

42:19.520 --> 42:22.560
<font color="#ffffff">And tonight we will celebrate</font>
<font color="#ffffff">the signing of our agreement.</font>

42:41.200 --> 42:42.240
<font color="#ffff00">No.</font>

42:43.600 --> 42:45.480
<font color="#ffff00">Please.</font>

42:45.480 --> 42:48.000
<font color="#ffff00">Don't take him away.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Let me talk to the king.</font>

42:48.000 --> 42:50.680
<font color="#00ff00">It is the law of the palace,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Your Highness. I'm sorry.</font>

42:54.400 --> 42:56.680
<font color="#ffff00">Get your hands off him!</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Your Highness!</font>

43:03.000 --> 43:07.360
<font color="#ffff00">Take him away</font>
<font color="#ffff00">and you take away my heart.</font>

43:07.360 --> 43:10.080
<font color="#00ff00">This is no place for children,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Your Highness.</font>

43:18.600 --> 43:20.400
<font color="#ffffff">It is for the best.</font>

43:36.040 --> 43:37.800
<font color="#ffffff">People of Paris,</font>

43:37.800 --> 43:42.560
<font color="#ffffff">I am here to remind you</font>
<font color="#ffffff">of the shared vision</font>

43:42.560 --> 43:45.000
<font color="#ffffff">that binds us all together...</font>

43:45.000 --> 43:48.200
<font color="#ffffff">..and of the wonder of our king,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Louis.</font>

43:49.960 --> 43:52.680
<font color="#ffffff">You have chosen to</font>
<font color="#ffffff">question his authority.</font>

43:52.680 --> 43:56.560
<font color="#ffffff">Our great king</font>
<font color="#ffffff">has only one purpose -</font>

43:56.560 --> 43:58.560
<font color="#ffffff">to further the glory of France.</font>

44:00.280 --> 44:04.200
<font color="#ffffff">But we all must make sacrifices,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">just as he does.</font>

44:04.200 --> 44:07.120
<font color="#ffffff">We must believe as he does,</font>

44:07.120 --> 44:09.240
<font color="#ffffff">dream as he does,</font>

44:09.240 --> 44:11.240
<font color="#ffffff">suffer as he does.</font>

44:13.000 --> 44:17.440
<font color="#ffffff">We must trust in him</font>
<font color="#ffffff">as he trusts in us.</font>

44:17.440 --> 44:21.400
<font color="#00ff00">Why should we trust him? So he can</font>
<font color="#00ff00">steal our money more easily?!</font>

44:23.280 --> 44:25.320
<font color="#ffffff">The king steals from no-one.</font>

44:25.320 --> 44:28.840
<font color="#ffffff">He raises taxes which he</font>
<font color="#ffffff">then returns to his people.</font>

44:28.840 --> 44:30.400
<font color="#ffffff">Look at his gifts.</font>

44:30.400 --> 44:35.840
<font color="#ffffff">Education, roads, clean water,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">street lighting, glory!</font>

44:35.840 --> 44:38.320
<font color="#00ff00">And poverty! </font><font color="#00ffff">Glory, my arse!</font>

44:41.200 --> 44:42.560
<font color="#ffffff">Listen!</font>

44:42.560 --> 44:47.040
<font color="#ffffff">We all must do our duty,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">just as he does his!</font>

44:56.800 --> 45:00.480
<font color="#ffffff">Leopold has offered</font>
<font color="#ffffff">80% of Spain and its possessions,</font>

45:00.480 --> 45:03.240
<font color="#ffffff">but I need the weight</font>
<font color="#ffffff">of the Vatican behind it.</font>

45:03.240 --> 45:05.920
<font color="#ffffff">You will go to Rome to</font>
<font color="#ffffff">ensure their support.</font>

45:05.920 --> 45:07.960
<font color="#00ff00">As you wish, Sire. But...</font>

45:07.960 --> 45:11.280
<font color="#ffffff">Remind the Pope where his loyalties</font>
<font color="#ffffff">should lie and remind him</font>

45:11.280 --> 45:15.360
<font color="#ffffff">that the bastion of the Catholic</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Church is France, not Vienna.</font>

45:15.360 --> 45:18.480
<font color="#00ff00">Sire, I cannot see</font>
<font color="#00ff00">what sort of influence</font>

45:18.480 --> 45:21.120
<font color="#00ff00">I could expect to have</font>
<font color="#00ff00">over his Holiness.</font>

45:21.120 --> 45:23.920
<font color="#ffffff">If you're convinced the journey</font>
<font color="#ffffff">is a waste of your time</font>

45:23.920 --> 45:26.400
<font color="#ffffff">then by all means remain here.</font>

45:26.400 --> 45:27.920
<font color="#ffffff">You could make yourself useful</font>

45:27.920 --> 45:30.880
<font color="#ffffff">by drawing up a list of suitable</font>
<font color="#ffffff">candidates to replace you.</font>

45:36.440 --> 45:38.800
<font color="#00ff00">The king must be informed. </font><font color="#ffff00">No.</font>

45:38.800 --> 45:40.640
<font color="#ffff00">If you discuss the matter with him,</font>

45:40.640 --> 45:43.160
<font color="#ffff00">he will order you to stop</font>
<font color="#ffff00">this investigation. </font><font color="#00ff00">Why?</font>

45:44.280 --> 45:48.280
<font color="#ffff00">In part because he believes it to be</font>
<font color="#ffff00">a figment of my imagination. </font><font color="#00ff00">And?</font>

45:55.880 --> 45:58.680
<font color="#ffff00">Give us a few more days</font>
<font color="#ffff00">before informing him.</font>

45:58.680 --> 46:02.160
<font color="#00ff00">Your Highness, you compromise me.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Then tell him.</font>

46:05.560 --> 46:06.760
<font color="#00ff00">A few days then.</font>

46:08.840 --> 46:12.480
<font color="#ffffff">Did you know that the Spanish</font>
<font color="#ffffff">word for cavalier is caballero</font>

46:12.480 --> 46:14.920
<font color="#ffffff">and the word for</font>
<font color="#ffffff">tresses is cabellera.</font>

46:14.920 --> 46:17.080
<font color="#ffffff">And she told me all about the men.</font>

46:17.080 --> 46:19.240
<font color="#ffffff">Very passionate, apparently.</font>

46:19.240 --> 46:22.120
<font color="#ffffff">Do we have to return to Vienna?</font>

46:22.120 --> 46:23.640
<font color="#ffffff">Can't we go to Spain?</font>

46:23.640 --> 46:26.080
<font color="#00ffff">We are going to Spain. </font><font color="#ffffff">Splendid.</font>

46:26.080 --> 46:29.000
<font color="#ffffff">Just as long as</font>
<font color="#ffffff">I don't meet the king.</font>

46:29.000 --> 46:32.840
<font color="#ffffff">You should see his portrait.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Oh, you will meet him. </font><font color="#ffffff">But why?</font>

46:39.600 --> 46:42.560
<font color="#00ffff">Because you're going to marry him.</font>

46:42.560 --> 46:44.800
<font color="#00ffff">Your mother's already</font>
<font color="#00ffff">on her way to Madrid.</font>

46:44.800 --> 46:48.840
<font color="#00ffff">We'll meet her there in three</font>
<font color="#00ffff">weeks' time. We leave tomorrow.</font>

46:48.840 --> 46:50.280
<font color="#ffffff">I refuse.</font>

46:51.440 --> 46:53.920
<font color="#ffffff">If you think I'm going to</font>
<font color="#ffffff">marry that hideous...</font>

46:58.920 --> 47:00.560
<font color="#00ffff">You will be queen of Spain.</font>

47:02.960 --> 47:04.480
<font color="#00ffff">You should be grateful.</font>

47:14.000 --> 47:17.480
<font color="#00ff00">Sire! Sire, a small matter</font>
<font color="#00ff00">which may be of interest.</font>

47:17.480 --> 47:20.200
<font color="#00ff00">We have received</font>
<font color="#00ff00">a report from Perpignan.</font>

47:20.200 --> 47:24.520
<font color="#00ff00">A cavalcade of Austrian nobles has</font>
<font color="#00ff00">been spotted crossing into Spain.</font>

47:24.520 --> 47:27.000
<font color="#ffffff">Do we know why? </font><font color="#00ff00">No, Sire.</font>

47:27.000 --> 47:29.320
<font color="#00ff00">A family gathering perhaps.</font>

47:29.320 --> 47:32.200
<font color="#ffffff">And why do families gather?</font>
<font color="#00ff00">For funerals.</font>

47:33.440 --> 47:35.040
<font color="#ffffff">And weddings.</font>

47:54.400 --> 47:56.680
<font color="#ffff00">Your Highness.</font>

47:56.680 --> 47:59.160
<font color="#00ffff">What a relief to see</font>
<font color="#00ffff">the face of a true friend.</font>

47:59.160 --> 48:02.120
<font color="#00ffff">Where have you been?</font>
<font color="#ffff00">In a convent.</font>

48:02.120 --> 48:05.760
<font color="#00ffff">Well, I am pleased</font>
<font color="#00ffff">to see you returned.</font>

48:05.760 --> 48:08.760
<font color="#ffff00">The last time I saw you,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">you were expecting a child.</font>

48:08.760 --> 48:11.840
<font color="#ffff00">May I ask...? </font><font color="#00ffff">A son. Philippe.</font>

48:13.040 --> 48:15.040
<font color="#ffff00">Where is he now?</font>

48:15.040 --> 48:16.360
<font color="#00ffff">Taken from me.</font>

48:17.720 --> 48:19.400
<font color="#ffff00">On whose orders?</font>

48:27.240 --> 48:28.680
<font color="#ffffff">The king!</font>

48:43.920 --> 48:44.960
<font color="#ffff00">Louis...</font>

48:46.560 --> 48:49.320
<font color="#ffff00">..your hospitality is</font>
<font color="#ffff00">the envy of the world.</font>

48:49.320 --> 48:50.560
<font color="#ffffff">I thank you.</font>

48:56.160 --> 48:58.760
<font color="#ffffff">I think you'll find</font>
<font color="#ffffff">everything in order.</font>

48:58.760 --> 49:00.200
<font color="#ffff00">It is all as we agreed?</font>

49:01.840 --> 49:04.080
<font color="#ffffff">Incidentally, a small matter.</font>

49:04.080 --> 49:06.840
<font color="#ffffff">Your niece, Eleanor. </font><font color="#ffff00">Yes?</font>

49:06.840 --> 49:09.520
<font color="#ffffff">I would like her to remain here</font>
<font color="#ffffff">with us at Versailles.</font>

49:12.080 --> 49:16.000
<font color="#ffff00">I'm sure she'd prefer to return</font>
<font color="#ffff00">to her family in Vienna.</font>

49:16.000 --> 49:17.760
<font color="#ffffff">And she will do so very soon.</font>

49:17.760 --> 49:19.960
<font color="#ffffff">In the meantime, let her stay here.</font>

49:19.960 --> 49:22.520
<font color="#ffffff">We shall show her</font>
<font color="#ffffff">all the wonders of Versailles.</font>

49:22.520 --> 49:24.760
<font color="#ffff00">It's a kind offer, but...</font>

49:24.760 --> 49:27.760
<font color="#ffffff">My wife has conceived</font>
<font color="#ffffff">an affection for the princess.</font>

49:29.720 --> 49:32.000
<font color="#ffffff">She would enjoy her</font>
<font color="#ffffff">company for a few months.</font>

49:32.000 --> 49:34.360
<font color="#ffffff">Would that please you?</font>

49:34.360 --> 49:35.480
<font color="#00ffff">Yes, Sire.</font>

49:36.680 --> 49:38.160
<font color="#ffffff">Then it's settled.</font>

49:38.160 --> 49:41.360
<font color="#ffffff">I give my word that she</font>
<font color="#ffffff">will be well looked after.</font>

49:41.360 --> 49:44.680
<font color="#ffffff">Who knows?</font>
<font color="#ffffff">We may even find her a husband.</font>

49:46.040 --> 49:47.720
<font color="#ffff00">As you wish.</font>

49:58.160 --> 50:00.400
<font color="#ffffff">Ladies and gentlemen of the court,</font>

50:00.400 --> 50:04.880
<font color="#ffffff">tomorrow we say farewell to someone</font>
<font color="#ffffff">who, two weeks ago, was an enemy.</font>

50:04.880 --> 50:07.640
<font color="#ffffff">Blood has been replaced by wine,</font>

50:07.640 --> 50:09.880
<font color="#ffffff">war by peace.</font>

50:09.880 --> 50:12.000
<font color="#ffffff">We are now allies</font>

50:12.000 --> 50:13.560
<font color="#ffffff">and friends.</font>

50:13.560 --> 50:15.200
<font color="#ffffff">APPLAUSE</font>

50:20.560 --> 50:26.640
<font color="#00ff00">A volunteer, please! Somebody</font>
<font color="#00ff00">willing to make a fool of himself.</font>

50:26.640 --> 50:29.840
<font color="#00ff00">The forthcoming, a favourite</font>
<font color="#00ff00">pastime of the Duc d'Orleans,</font>

50:29.840 --> 50:32.600
<font color="#00ff00">were he not sadly absent.</font>

50:33.960 --> 50:35.360
<font color="#00ff00">Louvois!</font>

50:36.840 --> 50:40.760
<font color="#00ff00">On second thoughts...perhaps</font>
<font color="#00ff00">someone a little more sprightly.</font>

50:42.160 --> 50:43.920
<font color="#ffffff">I shall take his place.</font>

50:50.960 --> 50:53.160
<font color="#00ff00">A brave proposition from the king.</font>

50:55.160 --> 50:57.960
<font color="#00ff00">Do I need to remind</font>
<font color="#00ff00">His Majesty of the rules?</font>

50:59.480 --> 51:00.840
<font color="#ffffff">No.</font>

51:00.840 --> 51:02.400
<font color="#00ff00">Ole!</font>

51:13.080 --> 51:14.520
<font color="#00ff00">Sire?</font>

51:21.400 --> 51:23.720
<font color="#ffff00">You heard what the king said?</font>

51:23.720 --> 51:24.760
